|0 |PX COORDINATOR MERGE SORT                        |                     |199     |72          |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                             |:EX10003             |199     |11          |
|2 |  └─SORT                                         |                     |199     |11          |
|3 |    └─HASH GROUP BY                              |                     |199     |11          |
|4 |      └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR                        |                     |300     |11          |
|5 |        └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)              |:EX10002             |300     |11          |
|6 |          └─MATERIAL                             |                     |300     |11          |
|7 |            └─HASH GROUP BY                      |                     |300     |11          |
|8 |              └─HASH RIGHT OUTER JOIN            |                     |300     |10          |
|9 |                ├─SUBPLAN SCAN                   |VIEW1                |199     |10          |
|10|                │ └─HASH GROUP BY                |                     |199     |10          |
|11|                │   └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |                     |2720    |9           |
|12|                │     └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)|:EX10000             |2720    |7           |
|13|                │       └─HASH GROUP BY          |                     |2720    |3           |
|14|                │         └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR    |                     |2755    |1           |
|15|                │           └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |orders               |2755    |1           |
|16|                └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR              |                     |300     |1           |
|17|                  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)    |:EX10001             |300     |1           |
|18|                    └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR          |                     |300     |1           |
|19|                      └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |customer(i_c_custkey)|300     |1           |
==================================================================================================
